title: Bejeweled 2 Deluxe

notes: Runs in software mode only due to NVIDIA ION GPU being incompatible with Vulkan enabled NVIDIA drivers. May work with hardware acceleration on other systems with supported video cards. Custom cursor is very slow. Using Alt+Tab causes the game to freeze and the Super key causes the desktop environment to black screen. Otherwise the game is perfectly playable using all modes with 100% performance in full screen and window mode on a 2010 Intel Atom CPU. Given the above, there are no graphical or audio issues.
